    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-07-25T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-07-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="158" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d158">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. McKee</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Burton</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 17.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Consulate United States of America
                                        at Panama</hi>, <hi rend="italic">United States of
                                        Colombia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-07-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 25,
                                1865.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the
                            receipt of your despatch No. 23, covering enclosure to the commander of
                            the naval forces in this port. Immediately on receipt I transmitted
                            enclosure to Commander Murray, senior officer now in the bay of
                            Panama.</p>
                <p>I also communicated contents of your despatch, <hi rend="italic">confidentially</hi>, as authorized by you, to General
                            Gutierrez.</p>
                <p>All quiet; how long it may so continue I am unable to inform you.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>ALEX. E. McKEE, <hi rend="italic">United States Consul</hi>,
                                    &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. A. A. <hi rend="smallcaps">Burton</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Minister Resident of the United States of America,
                                Bogota</hi>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
